.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/Blosc/c-blosc2/pull/634.patch","merged_at":"2024-10-23T18:19:07Z"},"body":"The `target_include_directories` interface is given in blosc2 subdirectory as `${CMAKE_CURRENT_SOURCE_DIR}`, which makes this directory automatically included when linking the blosc2 target in CMake. However, the blosc2 include directory is actually in the parent `../include` directory, so the correct way to include it could be `${CMAKE_CURRENT_SOURCE_DIR}/../include`. Moreover, `${CMAKE_CURRENT_SOURCE_DIR}` exposes internal headers instead of the public headers, so we may want to turn the original include directory into a private include.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Blosc/c-blosc2/issues/634/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Blosc/c-blosc2/issues/634/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"comment":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Blosc/c-blosc2/issues/comments/2433531367","html_url":"https://github.com/Blosc/c-blosc2/pull/634#issuecomment-2433531367","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Blosc/c-blosc2/issues/634","id":2433531367,"node_id":"IC_kwDOAmfImc6RDL3n","user":{"login":"dmikushin","id":5672874,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjU2NzI4NzQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5672874?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmikushin","html_url":"https://github.com/dmikushin","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmikushin/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmikushin/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmikushin/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmikushin/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmikushin/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmikushin/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dmikushin/rep